OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's choir wins Britain's
OL,4,CGot Talent
OL,6,FA choir put together by TV presenter
OL,7,FJeremy Clarkson has been named the
OL,8,Fwinner of the 2026 edition of
OL,9,FBritain's Got Talent.
OL,11,FThe Hawkstone Farmers' Choir was set
OL,12,Fup to support farmers around his farm
OL,13,Fin Chadlington, Oxfordshire, with
OL,14,Ftheir mental health, and is the first
OL,15,Fgroup of its kind to win the ITV
OL,16,Ftalent show.
OL,18,FThe Clarkson's Farm presenter, 66,
OL,19,Flooking emotional and applauding as
OL,20,Fthey performed during Saturday's live
OL,21,Ffinal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
