PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780240300
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's choir wins Britain's
OL,4,CGot Talent
OL,6,FAfter their win was announced, one of
OL,7,Fthe choir's members, Katryna Shell,
OL,8,Ftold presenters Ant McPartlin and
OL,9,FDeclan Donnelly: "We are the first
OL,10,Fever choir to have won Britain's Got
OL,11,FTalent.
OL,13,F"This is for all the farmers out
OL,14,Fthere, for anybody that's struggling,
OL,15,Fit's not a taboo subject, if you're
OL,16,Fnot OK, speak up, this is for the
OL,17,Ffarmers."
OL,19,FFans gathered at the The Farmer's Dog
OL,20,FPub to watch the choir crowned winners.
OL,26,@qD@ROUuD@AOUyD@IO]
