PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780240300
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's choir wins Britain's
OL,4,CGot Talent
OL,6,FThey will receive a #250,000 cash
OL,7,Fprize and the opportunity to perform
OL,8,Fat the annual Royal Variety
OL,9,FPerformance.
OL,11,FBefore their performance, the group
OL,12,Fdescribed Clarkson as their "biggest
OL,13,Fcheerleader" and added they "couldn't
OL,14,Fthank him enough", while judge KSI,
OL,15,Freal name Olajide Olatunji, said he
OL,16,Fwanted to add their original song,
OL,17,FThis Is Home, to his Spotify playlist
OL,18,Fafter they performed it.
