PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780240300
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's choir wins Britain's
OL,4,CGot Talent
OL,6,FJudge Simon Cowell said he had
OL,7,Fquestioned their decision to perform
OL,8,Fan original song, but told them "it
OL,9,Fpaid off" after their performance,
OL,10,Fcalling it "absolutely stunning",
OL,11,F"heartfelt" and "joyous", while fellow
OL,12,Fjudge Amanda Holden was brought to
OL,13,Ftears.
OL,26,@pD@aOUqD@IO]rD@LOUrD@`O]sD@AOUsD@KO]sD@
OL,26,AQOUsD@XO]
