PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780240300
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's choir wins Britain's
OL,4,CGot Talent
OL,6,FShe told them: "You've made me cry
OL,7,Fagain, I couldn't be prouder of you,
OL,8,Fthe harmonising was beautiful, and
OL,9,Fwatching the changing seasons behind
OL,10,Fyou, and really thinking about every
OL,11,Fsecond that you spend sowing dreams
OL,12,Finto that earth, which is one of the
OL,13,Fbeautiful lines of that song."
OL,15,FDog act Anastasiia and Salsa finished
OL,16,Fin third place, while drone display
OL,17,Fteam Celestial finished second after a
OL,18,Fpre-recorded performance recreating
OL,19,Fmoments from previous series of
OL,20,FBritain's Got Talent with illuminated
OL,21,Fdrones.
