OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780240300
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's choir wins Britain's
OL,4,CGot Talent
OL,6,FTeenage magician and musician Rafferty
OL,7,FCoope, from Winchester, came fifth
OL,8,Fafter also making in to the final.
OL,10,FShortly before the result was
OL,11,Fannounced, judge Alesha Dixon joined
OL,12,Fher newly reunited girl group Mis-
OL,13,FTeeq, completed by Sabrina Washington
OL,14,Fand Su-Elise Nash, for the first time
OL,15,Fin more than 20 years to perform a
OL,16,Fmedley of their hits including
OL,17,FScandalous.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
