PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780240300
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's choir wins Britain's
OL,4,CGot Talent
OL,6,FThe trio announced last week that they
OL,7,Fwould return to the stage for their
OL,8,FOne Night Stand gig at London's
OL,9,FWembley Arena on September 12.
OL,11,FFire-eater Liwei Yang opened the show
OL,12,Fwith a performance that saw her flip
OL,13,Fand dance with her husband with a
OL,14,Fblazing skipping rope, while her
OL,15,Fhusband also danced with two ropes of
OL,16,Ffire. It climaxed with her balancing a
OL,17,Fgiant flaming table in the air with
OL,18,Fher feet.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
