PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780240300
OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's choir wins Britain's
OL,4,CGot Talent
OL,6,FIt came after a delay to the programme
OL,7,Fwhile safety teams prepared the stage,
OL,8,Fwhile other performances included
OL,9,Fmagician and musician Rafferty Coope
OL,10,Fand poet Sonny Green.
